title: 107: The Lisa's Pantry Haul Episode
itunes:title: The Lisa's Pantry Haul Episode
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie head to Lisa’s pantry to test out some of her staples! Finds like xanthan gum (and how to use it), a tasty new puffed snack, THE BEST licorice ever, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the MUST-HAVE beverage that when added to other drinks, makes them 100 times better! But wait there’s more… a vegan hot dog that is surprisingly AMAZING! So go ahead and push play now. When you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for all the finds mentioned in the episode.
itunes:summary: This is the shortest traveled haul we’ve ever done… Lisa’s pantry!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
